Docker CE for Linux installation script - ubuntu
-----------------------------

Check already installed or not

run: docker

# This script is meant for quick & easy install via:

1. run: curl -fsSL https://get.docker.com -o get-docker.sh
2. run: sh get-docker.sh

If we want to give docker the root permission

run: sudo usermod -aG docker USER_NAME

Check:

run:	sudo docker version

